{"title_page": "Steak and Blowjob Day", "text_new": "{{short description|Unofficial observance}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=November 2018}}\n{{Infobox holiday\n|holiday_name  = Steak and Blowjob Day\n|type          = default\n|image         = \n|imagesize     = \n|caption       = \n|official_name = \n|nickname      = Steak and Knobber Day<br/>Steak & BJ Day\n|observedby    = [[North America]], [[Australia]], [[Europe]], [[New Zealand]]\n|litcolor      = \n|longtype      = Unofficial\n|significance  = [[Internet meme]]\n|begins        = \n|ends          = \n|date          = April 22nd\n|scheduling    = Same day each year\n|duration      = 1 day\n|frequency     = Annual\n|celebrations  = \n|observances   = [[Steak]], [[fellatio]]\n|relatedto     = [[Valentine's Day]]\n}}\n'''Steak and Blowjob Day''' (sometimes '''Steak & BJ Day''' or '''Steak and Knobber Day'''<ref name=dailydot2015>{{cite web |url=https://www.dailydot.com/unclick/steak-and-bj-day/ |title=The short, stupid history of 'Steak and a BJ Day' |last=Klee |first=Miles |date=March 14, 2015 |website= |publisher=[[The Daily Dot]] |access-date= February 5, 2018}}</ref>) is a satirical [[holiday]]<ref name=\"mirror\"/><ref name=\"bustle\">{{cite news |last=Sollee |first=Kristen |date=March 16, 2015 |title=These Satirical Tweets About \"Steak And BJ Day\" Are Comic Gold |url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/70053-these-satirical-tweets-about-steak-and-bj-day-are-comic-gold |url-status=live |newspaper=[[Bustle (magazine)|Bustle]] |access-date=January 16, 2018 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6wVdma8sk?url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/70053-these-satirical-tweets-about-steak-and-bj-day-are-comic-gold |archive-date=January 16, 2018 |df=mdy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Steak producer sets off tempest with racy \u2018man\u2019s day\u2019 marketing campaign  |url=https://nationalpost.com/pmn/news-pmn/canada-news-pmn/steak-producer-sets-off-facebook-feud-with-racy-mans-day-marketing-campaign |accessdate=11 March 2020 |agency=The Canadian Press |publisher=National Post |date=16 March 2018 |language=en-CA}}</ref> created in the United States as a male response to [[Valentine's Day]] and celebrated a month later, on [[March 14]].<ref name=\"hp\">{{cite web|url=http://www.houstonpress.com/restaurants/steak-and-a-bj-day-the-male-valentines-day-6416954|title=Steak and a BJ Day: The Male Valentine's Day|last=Shilcutt|first=Katherine|date=March 14, 2011|work=[[Houston Press]]|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref> On the day, women are purportedly supposed to cook a filet [[steak]] for and perform [[fellatio]] on a man in response to cards, [[chocolate]] and [[flower]]s given by men on Valentine's Day.<ref name=laweekly2013 /><ref name=stern />\n\nThe observance has no official status, being a popular [[Internet meme]] rather than an actual holiday, but various souvenirs and [[video clip]]s have been produced about it.<ref name=dailydot2015 /><ref name=sheknows2014 /> It was conceived in 2002 by DJ Tom Birdsey on [[WFNX]] radio.\n\nIt has been suggested that Steak and Blowjob Day is a backlash against the [[feminist movement]]; the holiday has been criticized as sexist and [[patriarchal]], though it has also been positively received by some, and used as a platform to fundraise for [[breast cancer research]].\n\n==History==\n\nSeveral websites<ref>Namely: [http://www.officialsteakandblowjobday.com/ officialsteakandblowjobday.com], [http://www.steakandbj.org/ steakandbj.org], [http://www.steakandbjday.com/ steakandbjday.com].</ref> claim to be the official site of Steak and Blowjob Day, but none of them identify as the creator. The sites concur that the holiday was devised by [[Radio personality|radio DJ]] Tom Birdsey in 2002, during a show on [[WFNX]] radio station in [[Boston]], [[Massachusetts]].<ref name=dailydot2015 /> One of the various websites competing to be the 'official' page of the day stated \"March 14th henceforth became 'Steak and Blowjob Day.' Simple, effective and self explanatory. No cards, no flowers, no special nights on the town; the name explains it all: just a steak and a BJ. That's it.\"<ref name=\"mnt\">{{cite web|url=http://www.miaminewtimes.com/restaurants/steak-and-bj-day-is-today-how-to-celebrate-in-miami-9201276|title=Steak and BJ Day Is Today: How to Celebrate|last=Doss|first=Laine|date=March 14, 2017|publisher=[[Miami New Times]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref>  The \"official\" websites provide guides on how [[Steak#Cooking|best to cook steak]], and how to best perform [[fellatio]].<ref name=\"q103\">{{cite web|url=http://q103albany.com/march-14th-is-steak-and-bj-day/|title=March 14th is Steak and BJ Day!|date=March 14, 2012|publisher=[[WPBZ-FM|Q103 Albany]]|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>\n\nThe day of celebration is sometimes suggested to be [[March 20]] instead of [[March 14]], either because the former was proclaimed to be Steak and Knobber Day by another radio host Dave Rickards in 1998, or because the latter coincides with [[Pi Day]],<ref name=dailydot2015 /><ref name=\"goth\">{{cite web|url=http://gothamist.com/2011/03/14/happy_steak_and_bj_day_or_pi_day_ne.php|title=Happy Steak And BJ Day! (Or Pi Day, Nerds)|last=Saxena|first=Jaya|date=March 14, 2011|publisher=[[Gothamist]]|access-date=January 16, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180307001826/http://gothamist.com/2011/03/14/happy_steak_and_bj_day_or_pi_day_ne.php|archive-date=March 7, 2018|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> which observes the [[mathematical constant]] [[Pi|{{pi}} (pi)]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2015/mar/13/pi-day-celebration-maths-fans-language-memory-contests|title=Pi Day 2015: a sweet treat for maths fans|last=Bellos|first=Alex|website=theguardian.com|date=March 14, 2015|accessdate=March 14, 2016}}</ref>\n\nA female equivalent of the day, is \"Cake and cunnilingus day\" on April 14.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2018/04/14/cake-and-cunnilingus-day-la-dolcissima-festa-del-sesso-orale-per-sole-donne/4293320/|title=Cake and Cunnilingus Day, la \"dolcissima\" festa del sesso orale per sole donne...|work=[[Il Fatto Quotidiano]]|language=Italian|date=14 April 2018|accessdate=3 December 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bild.de/unterhaltung/erotik/orale-sexualpraktiken/die-besten-cunnilingus-tipps-45353198/|title=Heute ist \u201eKuchen-und-Cunnilingus-Tag\"...|work=[[bild.de]]|language=German|date=14 April 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Cultural analysis==\n\nAccording to the [[women's history|women's historian]] [[Lois Banner]], the day appeared to be part of the backlash against the [[feminist movement]], moving toward a version of human interaction inherent to [[hookup culture]], and that men \"are really frightened because women are outperforming them\".<ref name=laweekly2013>{{cite web |url=http://www.laweekly.com/arts/its-steak-and-bj-day-should-we-be-offended-by-that-4184313 |title=It's Steak and BJ Day! Should We Be Offended By That? |last=Jones |first=Anna |date=March 14, 2013 |website=[[LA Weekly]] |access-date= |quote=}}</ref> Activist [[Feminista Jones]] argues that it limits women's [[freedom of choice]], thus being in the mainstream of traditional patriarchal restriction of [[Human female sexuality|female sexual behaviours]].<ref name=sheknows2014>{{cite web |url=http://www.sheknows.com/community/love/whats-deal-steak-and-blow-job-day-anyway |title=What's the Deal With \"Steak and Blow Job Day\"? |last=Jones |first=Feminista |author-link=Feminista Jones| date=2014 |website= |publisher=[[SheKnows Media]] |access-date= |quote=}}</ref> The [[sexual education|sexual educator]] Walker Thornton wrote that the day, although silly, emphasized for her the issues she had with the modern worldview of [[Valentine's Day]].<ref name=\"walker\">{{cite web|url=https://walkerthornton.com/steak-and-blowjob-day/|title=Men Get Their Own Day|last=Thornton|first=Walker|date=March 13, 2015|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>  ''[[Men's Health]]'' was unsure whether the holiday was actually celebrated, or whether the whole thing was a joke.<ref name=\"mh\">{{cite web|url=https://www.menshealth.com/sex-women/steak-and-blowjob-day|title=Yes, Steak and Blowjob Day Is a Real \"Holiday\"|last=Nu\u00f1ez|first=Alanna|date=February 27, 2017|work=[[Men's Health]]|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref> Spanish soccer newspaper ''[[Diario AS]]'' considers the holiday to be \"surreal\".<ref name=\"diarioas\">{{cite web|url=https://as.com/epik/2017/03/14/portada/1489505785_992519.html|title=D\u00eda internacional del solomillo: confesiones de un vegano imaginario|last=Garc\u00eda|first=Irene Sierra|date=March 14, 2017|publisher=[[Diario AS]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref> Student newspaper ''[[The Brown Daily Herald]]'' discussed the [[identity politics|gender and sexual]] political implications surrounding the meme, suggesting that fellatio is considered by many to be a job the giver must endure as opposed to a form of enjoyment, and in the framing of Steak and Blowjob Day as a \"man\u2019s holiday\" aimed at obtaining payback for Valentine's Day, this is perpetuated.<ref name=\"bdh\">{{cite web|url=http://post.browndailyherald.com/2014/04/23/a-feminist-defense-of-blowjobs/|title=A Feminist Defense of Blowjobs|date=April 23, 2014|work=[[The Brown Daily Herald]]|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Reception==\n\nLifestyle blog ''[[YourTango]]'' felt the idea of such a holiday was an enshrining of [[male privilege]] and was, like Valentine's Day, a \"silly calendar filler\".<ref name=\"tango\">{{cite web|url=https://www.yourtango.com/2017300761/steak-and-bj-day-symbol-male-privilege-or-feminist-opportunity|title=Is A Steak And BJ Day A Symbol Of Male Privilege Or Feminist Opportunity?|last=Jeret|first=Arianna|date=March 14, 2017|work=[[Tango (magazine)|Tango]]|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref> ''[[The Huffington Post]]'' stated that the day \"made them want to gag\",<ref name=\"huffpo\">{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/14/steak-and-blow-job-day-today-march-14_n_2869619.html|title=Steak And BJ Day Makes Us Want To Gag|date=March 14, 2014|work=[[The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref> and ''[[FHM (magazine)|FHM]]'' and the ''[[Daily Mirror]]'' noted that businesses were cashing in on the unofficial holiday.<ref name=\"fhm\">{{cite web|url=http://www.fhm.com/posts/how-to-make-the-most-of-your-steak-and-a-bj-day-127707/photos/primal-cut-240111|title=How To Make The Most Of Your Steak And A BJ Day|date=March 14, 2017|publisher=[[FHM (magazine)|FHM Online]]|accessdate=January 17, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"mirror\">{{cite web|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/steak-bj-day-2015-valentines-5335934|title=Steak and BJ Day 2015: 'Valentine's Day for men' is happening today across the world|last=Raven|first=David|date=March 14, 2015|work=[[Daily Mirror]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref>\n\nThe concept of a men's movement<ref name=\"dans\">{{cite web|url=https://www.avclub.com/dan-savage-1798308285|title=Dan Savage|last=Robinson|first=Tasha|date=February 8, 2006|website=[[The A.V. Club]]|accessdate=February 13, 2018}}</ref> looking to create such a day has caused some controversy and incited opposition,<ref name=\"desouza\">{{cite web|url=https://www.news24.com/Columnists/Archive/SerenadeSouza/Its-Singles-Bashing-Day-today-20050214|title=It's Singles-Bashing Day Today|last=De Souza|first=Serena|date=February 14, 2005|publisher=[[News24.com]]|accessdate=February 13, 2018}}</ref> being described as [[Antifeminism|antifeminist]] or [[Patriarchy|patriarchal]].<ref name=\"horton\">{{cite web|url=https://ethicsbeyondcompliance.wordpress.com/2014/03/27/why-i-hate-steak-and-bj-day/|title=Why I hate Steak and BJ Day|last=Horton|first=Randall|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref> The men's magazine ''[[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim]]'' described it as the greatest holiday of all time,<ref name=\"maxim\">{{cite web|url=https://www.maxim.com/maxim-man/steak-and-blowjob-day-2017-2|title=There's an Actual Holiday Called Steak and Blowjob Day, and it's Almost Here|last=Yenisey|first=Zeynep|date=February 27, 2017|work=[[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim]]|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref> whereas ''[[Cosmopolitan (magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]'' was unsure whether it was an outdated and sexist event or a bawdy celebration of sex and food.<ref name=\"cosmo\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/sex-love/news/a37773/enjoy-the-best-tweets-from-steak-and-blow-job-day/|title=14 Absolutely Horrible Jokes From Men About \"Steak and Blow Job Day\"|last=Rose|first=Rebecca|date=March 14, 2015|publisher=[[Cosmopolitan (magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref> One opinion piece on the day suggested it was [[Neanderthals in popular culture|Neanderthal]] in trying to force through the idea of a day devoted to the combination of fellatio and steak, and suggested a range of alternatives.<ref name=\"sabo\">{{cite web|url=https://sabotagetimes.com/life/10-alternatives-to-steak-blowjob-day|title=10 Alternatives To Steak & Blowjob Day|date=March 14, 2014|publisher=[[Sabotage Times]]|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>\n\nThe holiday has drawn attention from celebrities including [[Christina Aguilera]], who encouraged her fans to celebrate it in 2014.<ref name=\"cag\">{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/21/christina-aguilera-steak-bj-day_n_5008193.html|title=Christina Aguilera Encourages Fans To Celebrate Steak And BJ Day|date=March 21, 2014|work=[[The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"eonline\">{{cite news |last=Toomey |first=Alyssa |date=March 21, 2014 |title=Christina Aguilera Celebrates \"Steak and BJ Day,\" Encourages Naughty Fans to Do the Same |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/523653/christina-aguilera-celebrates-steak-and-bj-day-encourages-naughty-fans-to-do-the-same |newspaper=[[E! Online]] |access-date=January 16, 2018 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6wVdruywB?url=http://www.eonline.com/news/523653/christina-aguilera-celebrates-steak-and-bj-day-encourages-naughty-fans-to-do-the-same |archive-date=January 16, 2018 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\nIn 2016, ''[[Instinct (magazine)|Instinct]]'' noted that the day is also now being used as a way to successfully [[fundraising|raise money]] for [[breast cancer research]].<ref name=\"instinct\">{{cite web|url=http://instinctmagazine.com/post/march-14th-international-steak-blowjob-day|title=March 14th is International Steak & Blowjob Day?|last=Dupuis|first=Adam|date=March 13, 2016|publisher=[[Instinct (magazine)|Instinct]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref>  In Germany, ''[[Bild]]'' noted the day is known as ''Schnitzel und Blowjob Tag'',<ref name=\"bild\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bild.de/10um10/2012/gedenktag/aktion-schnitzel-blowjob-sinnlos-welt-23111748.bild.html|title=10 v\u00f6llig sinnlose Aktionstage (\"10 completely senseless action days\"|date=March 14, 2012|publisher=[[Bild]]|language=German|accessdate=January 25, 2018}}</ref> or ''Schniblo'' for short,<ref name=\"stern\">{{cite web|url=https://www.stern.de/familie/henriette-hell/-valentinstag---maenner--langsam-muesst-ihr-euch-den--schnitzel---blowjob--tag-verdienen--7837626.html|title=Valentinstag \u2013 M\u00e4nner, langsam m\u00fcsst ihr euch den \"Schnitzel & Blowjob\"-Tag verdienen!|last=Hell|first=Henriette|date=January 28, 2018|publisher=[[Stern (magazine)|Stern]]|language=German|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref> and in France, female-targeted magazine ''{{ill|MadmoiZelle|fr}}'' noted it was a day targeted at men,<ref name=\"mmz\">{{cite web|url=http://www.madmoizelle.com/steak-bj-day-32802|title=Un steak et une pipe, la r\u00e9plique masculine \u00e0 la St Val|last=Florent|first=Fab|date=March 14, 2011|work=MadmoiZelle|language=French|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref> while ''{{ill|Le Bonbon|fr}}'' said it was a \"most American holiday\".<ref name=\"lebonbon\">{{cite web|url=https://www.lebonbon.fr/nuit/nuit-18-18/steak-gaterie-la-journee-de-lhomme/|title='Steak & g\u00e2terie', la journ\u00e9e de l'homme!|last=Znaty|first=Simon Kinski|date=September 1, 2015|work=LeBonBon|language=French|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>  In Spain, daily newspaper ''[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]]'' noted in Spain it would be called ''D\u00eda del Solomillo y el Sexo Oral'' and that the day joined food and sex, which it opined were two of the greatest pleasures in the world.<ref name=\"elmundo\">{{cite web|url=http://www.elmundo.es/f5/comparte/2017/03/14/58c6d09de2704ed43a8b457e.html|title=14 de marzo, D\u00eda del Solomillo y el Sexo Oral, y otras cuatro citas carnales para marcar en rojo en el calendario|last=Bermejo|first=Diego|date=March 14, 2017|work=[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Pi Day]]\n* [[White Day]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{cite web |url=http://veganfeministnetwork.com/steak-bj-day/ |title=Steak & BJ Day: Because Women\u2019s Cancer is All about Pleasing Men |last= |first= |date=March 14, 2015 |website= |publisher=Vegan Feminist Network |access-date= |quote=}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://schni-blo.de |title=Der internationale Schnitzel und Blowjob Tag findet immer mehr Anh\u00e4nger in Deutschland |last= |first= |date=March 14, 2018 |website= |publisher=Markus Waibel |access-date= |quote=}}\n\n[[Category:March observances]]\n[[Category:Steak]]\n[[Category:Observances in the United States]]\n[[Category:Observances in Germany]]\n[[Category:Unofficial observances]]\n[[Category:Off-color humor]]\n[[Category:Fellatio]]\n[[Category:Internet memes]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Unofficial observance}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=November 2018}}\n{{Infobox holiday\n|holiday_name  = Steak and Blowjob Day\n|type          = default\n|image         = \n|imagesize     = \n|caption       = \n|official_name = \n|nickname      = Steak and Knobber Day<br/>Steak & BJ Day\n|observedby    = [[North America]], [[Australia]], [[Europe]], [[New Zealand]]\n|litcolor      = \n|longtype      = Unofficial\n|significance  = [[Internet meme]]\n|begins        = \n|ends          = \n|date          = March 14\n|scheduling    = Same day each year\n|duration      = 1 day\n|frequency     = Annual\n|celebrations  = \n|observances   = [[Steak]], [[fellatio]]\n|relatedto     = [[Valentine's Day]]\n}}\n'''Steak and Blowjob Day''' (sometimes '''Steak & BJ Day''' or '''Steak and Knobber Day'''<ref name=dailydot2015>{{cite web |url=https://www.dailydot.com/unclick/steak-and-bj-day/ |title=The short, stupid history of 'Steak and a BJ Day' |last=Klee |first=Miles |date=March 14, 2015 |website= |publisher=[[The Daily Dot]] |access-date= February 5, 2018}}</ref>) is a satirical [[holiday]]<ref name=\"mirror\"/><ref name=\"bustle\">{{cite news |last=Sollee |first=Kristen |date=March 16, 2015 |title=These Satirical Tweets About \"Steak And BJ Day\" Are Comic Gold |url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/70053-these-satirical-tweets-about-steak-and-bj-day-are-comic-gold |url-status=live |newspaper=[[Bustle (magazine)|Bustle]] |access-date=January 16, 2018 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6wVdma8sk?url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/70053-these-satirical-tweets-about-steak-and-bj-day-are-comic-gold |archive-date=January 16, 2018 |df=mdy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Steak producer sets off tempest with racy \u2018man\u2019s day\u2019 marketing campaign  |url=https://nationalpost.com/pmn/news-pmn/canada-news-pmn/steak-producer-sets-off-facebook-feud-with-racy-mans-day-marketing-campaign |accessdate=11 March 2020 |agency=The Canadian Press |publisher=National Post |date=16 March 2018 |language=en-CA}}</ref> created in the United States as a male response to [[Valentine's Day]] and celebrated a month later, on [[March 14]].<ref name=\"hp\">{{cite web|url=http://www.houstonpress.com/restaurants/steak-and-a-bj-day-the-male-valentines-day-6416954|title=Steak and a BJ Day: The Male Valentine's Day|last=Shilcutt|first=Katherine|date=March 14, 2011|work=[[Houston Press]]|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref> On the day, women are purportedly supposed to cook a filet [[steak]] for and perform [[fellatio]] on a man in response to cards, [[chocolate]] and [[flower]]s given by men on Valentine's Day.<ref name=laweekly2013 /><ref name=stern />\n\nThe observance has no official status, being a popular [[Internet meme]] rather than an actual holiday, but various souvenirs and [[video clip]]s have been produced about it.<ref name=dailydot2015 /><ref name=sheknows2014 /> It was conceived in 2002 by DJ Tom Birdsey on [[WFNX]] radio.\n\nIt has been suggested that Steak and Blowjob Day is a backlash against the [[feminist movement]]; the holiday has been criticized as sexist and [[patriarchal]], though it has also been positively received by some, and used as a platform to fundraise for [[breast cancer research]].\n\n==History==\n\nSeveral websites<ref>Namely: [http://www.officialsteakandblowjobday.com/ officialsteakandblowjobday.com], [http://www.steakandbj.org/ steakandbj.org], [http://www.steakandbjday.com/ steakandbjday.com].</ref> claim to be the official site of Steak and Blowjob Day, but none of them identify as the creator. The sites concur that the holiday was devised by [[Radio personality|radio DJ]] Tom Birdsey in 2002, during a show on [[WFNX]] radio station in [[Boston]], [[Massachusetts]].<ref name=dailydot2015 /> One of the various websites competing to be the 'official' page of the day stated \"March 14th henceforth became 'Steak and Blowjob Day.' Simple, effective and self explanatory. No cards, no flowers, no special nights on the town; the name explains it all: just a steak and a BJ. That's it.\"<ref name=\"mnt\">{{cite web|url=http://www.miaminewtimes.com/restaurants/steak-and-bj-day-is-today-how-to-celebrate-in-miami-9201276|title=Steak and BJ Day Is Today: How to Celebrate|last=Doss|first=Laine|date=March 14, 2017|publisher=[[Miami New Times]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref>  The \"official\" websites provide guides on how [[Steak#Cooking|best to cook steak]], and how to best perform [[fellatio]].<ref name=\"q103\">{{cite web|url=http://q103albany.com/march-14th-is-steak-and-bj-day/|title=March 14th is Steak and BJ Day!|date=March 14, 2012|publisher=[[WPBZ-FM|Q103 Albany]]|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>\n\nThe day of celebration is sometimes suggested to be [[March 20]] instead of [[March 14]], either because the former was proclaimed to be Steak and Knobber Day by another radio host Dave Rickards in 1998, or because the latter coincides with [[Pi Day]],<ref name=dailydot2015 /><ref name=\"goth\">{{cite web|url=http://gothamist.com/2011/03/14/happy_steak_and_bj_day_or_pi_day_ne.php|title=Happy Steak And BJ Day! (Or Pi Day, Nerds)|last=Saxena|first=Jaya|date=March 14, 2011|publisher=[[Gothamist]]|access-date=January 16, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180307001826/http://gothamist.com/2011/03/14/happy_steak_and_bj_day_or_pi_day_ne.php|archive-date=March 7, 2018|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> which observes the [[mathematical constant]] [[Pi|{{pi}} (pi)]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2015/mar/13/pi-day-celebration-maths-fans-language-memory-contests|title=Pi Day 2015: a sweet treat for maths fans|last=Bellos|first=Alex|website=theguardian.com|date=March 14, 2015|accessdate=March 14, 2016}}</ref>\n\nA female equivalent of the day, is \"Cake and cunnilingus day\" on April 14.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2018/04/14/cake-and-cunnilingus-day-la-dolcissima-festa-del-sesso-orale-per-sole-donne/4293320/|title=Cake and Cunnilingus Day, la \"dolcissima\" festa del sesso orale per sole donne...|work=[[Il Fatto Quotidiano]]|language=Italian|date=14 April 2018|accessdate=3 December 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bild.de/unterhaltung/erotik/orale-sexualpraktiken/die-besten-cunnilingus-tipps-45353198/|title=Heute ist \u201eKuchen-und-Cunnilingus-Tag\"...|work=[[bild.de]]|language=German|date=14 April 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Cultural analysis==\n\nAccording to the [[women's history|women's historian]] [[Lois Banner]], the day appeared to be part of the backlash against the [[feminist movement]], moving toward a version of human interaction inherent to [[hookup culture]], and that men \"are really frightened because women are outperforming them\".<ref name=laweekly2013>{{cite web |url=http://www.laweekly.com/arts/its-steak-and-bj-day-should-we-be-offended-by-that-4184313 |title=It's Steak and BJ Day! Should We Be Offended By That? |last=Jones |first=Anna |date=March 14, 2013 |website=[[LA Weekly]] |access-date= |quote=}}</ref> Activist [[Feminista Jones]] argues that it limits women's [[freedom of choice]], thus being in the mainstream of traditional patriarchal restriction of [[Human female sexuality|female sexual behaviours]].<ref name=sheknows2014>{{cite web |url=http://www.sheknows.com/community/love/whats-deal-steak-and-blow-job-day-anyway |title=What's the Deal With \"Steak and Blow Job Day\"? |last=Jones |first=Feminista |author-link=Feminista Jones| date=2014 |website= |publisher=[[SheKnows Media]] |access-date= |quote=}}</ref> The [[sexual education|sexual educator]] Walker Thornton wrote that the day, although silly, emphasized for her the issues she had with the modern worldview of [[Valentine's Day]].<ref name=\"walker\">{{cite web|url=https://walkerthornton.com/steak-and-blowjob-day/|title=Men Get Their Own Day|last=Thornton|first=Walker|date=March 13, 2015|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>  ''[[Men's Health]]'' was unsure whether the holiday was actually celebrated, or whether the whole thing was a joke.<ref name=\"mh\">{{cite web|url=https://www.menshealth.com/sex-women/steak-and-blowjob-day|title=Yes, Steak and Blowjob Day Is a Real \"Holiday\"|last=Nu\u00f1ez|first=Alanna|date=February 27, 2017|work=[[Men's Health]]|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref> Spanish soccer newspaper ''[[Diario AS]]'' considers the holiday to be \"surreal\".<ref name=\"diarioas\">{{cite web|url=https://as.com/epik/2017/03/14/portada/1489505785_992519.html|title=D\u00eda internacional del solomillo: confesiones de un vegano imaginario|last=Garc\u00eda|first=Irene Sierra|date=March 14, 2017|publisher=[[Diario AS]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref> Student newspaper ''[[The Brown Daily Herald]]'' discussed the [[identity politics|gender and sexual]] political implications surrounding the meme, suggesting that fellatio is considered by many to be a job the giver must endure as opposed to a form of enjoyment, and in the framing of Steak and Blowjob Day as a \"man\u2019s holiday\" aimed at obtaining payback for Valentine's Day, this is perpetuated.<ref name=\"bdh\">{{cite web|url=http://post.browndailyherald.com/2014/04/23/a-feminist-defense-of-blowjobs/|title=A Feminist Defense of Blowjobs|date=April 23, 2014|work=[[The Brown Daily Herald]]|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Reception==\n\nLifestyle blog ''[[YourTango]]'' felt the idea of such a holiday was an enshrining of [[male privilege]] and was, like Valentine's Day, a \"silly calendar filler\".<ref name=\"tango\">{{cite web|url=https://www.yourtango.com/2017300761/steak-and-bj-day-symbol-male-privilege-or-feminist-opportunity|title=Is A Steak And BJ Day A Symbol Of Male Privilege Or Feminist Opportunity?|last=Jeret|first=Arianna|date=March 14, 2017|work=[[Tango (magazine)|Tango]]|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref> ''[[The Huffington Post]]'' stated that the day \"made them want to gag\",<ref name=\"huffpo\">{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/14/steak-and-blow-job-day-today-march-14_n_2869619.html|title=Steak And BJ Day Makes Us Want To Gag|date=March 14, 2014|work=[[The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref> and ''[[FHM (magazine)|FHM]]'' and the ''[[Daily Mirror]]'' noted that businesses were cashing in on the unofficial holiday.<ref name=\"fhm\">{{cite web|url=http://www.fhm.com/posts/how-to-make-the-most-of-your-steak-and-a-bj-day-127707/photos/primal-cut-240111|title=How To Make The Most Of Your Steak And A BJ Day|date=March 14, 2017|publisher=[[FHM (magazine)|FHM Online]]|accessdate=January 17, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"mirror\">{{cite web|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/steak-bj-day-2015-valentines-5335934|title=Steak and BJ Day 2015: 'Valentine's Day for men' is happening today across the world|last=Raven|first=David|date=March 14, 2015|work=[[Daily Mirror]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref>\n\nThe concept of a men's movement<ref name=\"dans\">{{cite web|url=https://www.avclub.com/dan-savage-1798308285|title=Dan Savage|last=Robinson|first=Tasha|date=February 8, 2006|website=[[The A.V. Club]]|accessdate=February 13, 2018}}</ref> looking to create such a day has caused some controversy and incited opposition,<ref name=\"desouza\">{{cite web|url=https://www.news24.com/Columnists/Archive/SerenadeSouza/Its-Singles-Bashing-Day-today-20050214|title=It's Singles-Bashing Day Today|last=De Souza|first=Serena|date=February 14, 2005|publisher=[[News24.com]]|accessdate=February 13, 2018}}</ref> being described as [[Antifeminism|antifeminist]] or [[Patriarchy|patriarchal]].<ref name=\"horton\">{{cite web|url=https://ethicsbeyondcompliance.wordpress.com/2014/03/27/why-i-hate-steak-and-bj-day/|title=Why I hate Steak and BJ Day|last=Horton|first=Randall|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref> The men's magazine ''[[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim]]'' described it as the greatest holiday of all time,<ref name=\"maxim\">{{cite web|url=https://www.maxim.com/maxim-man/steak-and-blowjob-day-2017-2|title=There's an Actual Holiday Called Steak and Blowjob Day, and it's Almost Here|last=Yenisey|first=Zeynep|date=February 27, 2017|work=[[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim]]|accessdate=January 15, 2018}}</ref> whereas ''[[Cosmopolitan (magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]'' was unsure whether it was an outdated and sexist event or a bawdy celebration of sex and food.<ref name=\"cosmo\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/sex-love/news/a37773/enjoy-the-best-tweets-from-steak-and-blow-job-day/|title=14 Absolutely Horrible Jokes From Men About \"Steak and Blow Job Day\"|last=Rose|first=Rebecca|date=March 14, 2015|publisher=[[Cosmopolitan (magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref> One opinion piece on the day suggested it was [[Neanderthals in popular culture|Neanderthal]] in trying to force through the idea of a day devoted to the combination of fellatio and steak, and suggested a range of alternatives.<ref name=\"sabo\">{{cite web|url=https://sabotagetimes.com/life/10-alternatives-to-steak-blowjob-day|title=10 Alternatives To Steak & Blowjob Day|date=March 14, 2014|publisher=[[Sabotage Times]]|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>\n\nThe holiday has drawn attention from celebrities including [[Christina Aguilera]], who encouraged her fans to celebrate it in 2014.<ref name=\"cag\">{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/03/21/christina-aguilera-steak-bj-day_n_5008193.html|title=Christina Aguilera Encourages Fans To Celebrate Steak And BJ Day|date=March 21, 2014|work=[[The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"eonline\">{{cite news |last=Toomey |first=Alyssa |date=March 21, 2014 |title=Christina Aguilera Celebrates \"Steak and BJ Day,\" Encourages Naughty Fans to Do the Same |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/523653/christina-aguilera-celebrates-steak-and-bj-day-encourages-naughty-fans-to-do-the-same |newspaper=[[E! Online]] |access-date=January 16, 2018 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6wVdruywB?url=http://www.eonline.com/news/523653/christina-aguilera-celebrates-steak-and-bj-day-encourages-naughty-fans-to-do-the-same |archive-date=January 16, 2018 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\nIn 2016, ''[[Instinct (magazine)|Instinct]]'' noted that the day is also now being used as a way to successfully [[fundraising|raise money]] for [[breast cancer research]].<ref name=\"instinct\">{{cite web|url=http://instinctmagazine.com/post/march-14th-international-steak-blowjob-day|title=March 14th is International Steak & Blowjob Day?|last=Dupuis|first=Adam|date=March 13, 2016|publisher=[[Instinct (magazine)|Instinct]]|accessdate=January 16, 2018}}</ref>  In Germany, ''[[Bild]]'' noted the day is known as ''Schnitzel und Blowjob Tag'',<ref name=\"bild\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bild.de/10um10/2012/gedenktag/aktion-schnitzel-blowjob-sinnlos-welt-23111748.bild.html|title=10 v\u00f6llig sinnlose Aktionstage (\"10 completely senseless action days\"|date=March 14, 2012|publisher=[[Bild]]|language=German|accessdate=January 25, 2018}}</ref> or ''Schniblo'' for short,<ref name=\"stern\">{{cite web|url=https://www.stern.de/familie/henriette-hell/-valentinstag---maenner--langsam-muesst-ihr-euch-den--schnitzel---blowjob--tag-verdienen--7837626.html|title=Valentinstag \u2013 M\u00e4nner, langsam m\u00fcsst ihr euch den \"Schnitzel & Blowjob\"-Tag verdienen!|last=Hell|first=Henriette|date=January 28, 2018|publisher=[[Stern (magazine)|Stern]]|language=German|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref> and in France, female-targeted magazine ''{{ill|MadmoiZelle|fr}}'' noted it was a day targeted at men,<ref name=\"mmz\">{{cite web|url=http://www.madmoizelle.com/steak-bj-day-32802|title=Un steak et une pipe, la r\u00e9plique masculine \u00e0 la St Val|last=Florent|first=Fab|date=March 14, 2011|work=MadmoiZelle|language=French|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref> while ''{{ill|Le Bonbon|fr}}'' said it was a \"most American holiday\".<ref name=\"lebonbon\">{{cite web|url=https://www.lebonbon.fr/nuit/nuit-18-18/steak-gaterie-la-journee-de-lhomme/|title='Steak & g\u00e2terie', la journ\u00e9e de l'homme!|last=Znaty|first=Simon Kinski|date=September 1, 2015|work=LeBonBon|language=French|accessdate=January 26, 2018}}</ref>  In Spain, daily newspaper ''[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]]'' noted in Spain it would be called ''D\u00eda del Solomillo y el Sexo Oral'' and that the day joined food and sex, which it opined were two of the greatest pleasures in the world.<ref name=\"elmundo\">{{cite web|url=http://www.elmundo.es/f5/comparte/2017/03/14/58c6d09de2704ed43a8b457e.html|title=14 de marzo, D\u00eda del Solomillo y el Sexo Oral, y otras cuatro citas carnales para marcar en rojo en el calendario|last=Bermejo|first=Diego|date=March 14, 2017|work=[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=January 31, 2018}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Pi Day]]\n* [[White Day]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{cite web |url=http://veganfeministnetwork.com/steak-bj-day/ |title=Steak & BJ Day: Because Women\u2019s Cancer is All about Pleasing Men |last= |first= |date=March 14, 2015 |website= |publisher=Vegan Feminist Network |access-date= |quote=}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://schni-blo.de |title=Der internationale Schnitzel und Blowjob Tag findet immer mehr Anh\u00e4nger in Deutschland |last= |first= |date=March 14, 2018 |website= |publisher=Markus Waibel |access-date= |quote=}}\n\n[[Category:March observances]]\n[[Category:Steak]]\n[[Category:Observances in the United States]]\n[[Category:Observances in Germany]]\n[[Category:Unofficial observances]]\n[[Category:Off-color humor]]\n[[Category:Fellatio]]\n[[Category:Internet memes]]\n", "name_user": "Leonbonner82", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steak_and_Blowjob_Day"}
